                    <ab>fi[lius] quondam […] [...]ro[...] idest omnes res et p[er]ti[nentjas...] que
                        mihi pertinet in <rs key="#Fundi">fundo</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Venditio #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Forests #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder"
                            ref="#places/3544"><geogName key="#Venditio #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Forests #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder" ref="#estates/2445"
                                >A[rc]uada</geogName></placeName>; <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terris</rs>, [<rs key="#Wine">vin]eis</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals"
                            >campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder"
                            >pascuis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, <rs>salecti</rs> et cum
                        o[m]nibus sibi pertinentibus; a pressenti die liceat tibi tuisque filiis et
                        heredibus ipsa rem que superius legitur intro et preoccupare per a[c] <rs
                            key="#Venditio">paginam venditjonis</rs>. Et accepit <rs key="#Price"
                            >pretjum idest valente sol(idos) treinta den(ariorum) Veneticorum</rs>.
                        Et ego cum meis filiis et heredes tibi tuisque filiis et heredibus ipsa rem
                        que superius legitur ab omni persona hominum defensare et autoriare
                        promitto, supena <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi untjas duas</rs> et post
                        pena soll(utjonem) m(anente) hec pagina in sua firm(itate). Guilielmus de
                        Ve[...], Teudo filius quondam Alfrido, Ioh(anne)s [fi]l[i]us quondam
                        Bo[...], Ioh(anne)s f[ili]us quondam Ioh(anni)s [...] Dominicus,
                        [I]ustino.</ab>
                </div>
